External Libraries Setup
------------------------
Before compiling the project, some external libraries need to be compiled.

Compile adaptive quadrature library.
  cc -fPIC -O3 -c hquadrature.c -o adaptive_quadrature.o
  Copy adaptive_quadrature.o into the lib/ subdirectory.

Compile the Gaussian quadrature integration library.
  cc -fPIC -O3 -c gauss_legendre.c -o gaussian_quadrature.o
  Copy guassian_quadrature.o into the lib/ subdirectory.


